184
00:11:27,070 --> 00:11:28,710
but kept us in the dark?

185
00:11:29,990 --> 00:11:31,710
Xi, that's nonsense.

186
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:32,910
No matter what,

187
00:11:32,910 --> 00:11:34,830
