214
00:14:05,470 --> 00:14:06,640
to find out the truth,

215
00:14:06,640 --> 00:14:08,320
and then I'll go to Ning Zhaoxiong

216
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:10,180
to settle things once and for all.

217
00:14:10,310 --> 00:14:11,270
I'll go with you.

218
00:14:12,070 --> 00:14:12,800
Don't worry.

219
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:14,220
I won't rat you out.

220
00:14:15,110 --> 00:14:16,370
That's not what I mean.

221
00:14:16,990 --> 00:14:18,670
I just want to be there for you.

222
00:14:24,420 --> 00:14:25,950
This is my personal affair.

223
00:14:26,160 --> 00:14:27,420
