225
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:31,930
I'm already very grateful.

226
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:33,710
I don't want to put you on the spot in the Ning family

227
00:14:33,710 --> 00:14:35,000
because of this.

228
00:14:39,030 --> 00:14:41,230
Now that Ye Yunkai is out of the picture,

229
00:14:42,110 --> 00:14:44,070
