237
00:15:02,710 --> 00:15:04,510
You don't need to worry about me.

238
00:15:05,680 --> 00:15:06,980
Go to the PR department

239
00:15:07,470 --> 00:15:09,930
and have a word with our friends in the media.

240
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:12,350
Tell them to fan the flames a little bit

241
00:15:12,350 --> 00:15:16,150
and escalate Su Yu's plagiarism scandal.

242
00:15:16,300 --> 00:15:17,290
That way,

243
00:15:17,430 --> 00:15:19,230
