244
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:26,110
Su Yu's reputation has been ruined because of this scandal.

245
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:27,310
However,

246
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:30,000
with good PR,

247
00:15:31,070 --> 00:15:32,470
he's competent enough

248
00:15:32,940 --> 00:15:35,460
to make a comeback in the market

249
00:15:35,710 --> 00:15:39,130
