276
00:17:07,700 --> 00:17:09,020
to let you in.

277
00:17:09,230 --> 00:17:11,290
The negative public opinion about me

278
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:13,220
hasn't died down over time.

279
00:17:13,390 --> 00:17:14,970
Instead, it's gotten worse.

280
00:17:14,970 --> 00:17:15,520
Mr. Ning,

281
00:17:16,089 --> 00:17:18,290
that's exactly what you want, isn't it?

282
00:17:19,790 --> 00:17:20,720
What do you mean?

283
00:17:22,150 --> 00:17:23,800
You played the same old trick again.

284
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,599
It's indeed something you'd do.

285
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,040
What are you getting at?

286
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:28,550
Mr. Ning.

287
00:17:29,710 --> 00:17:31,500
Do you remember someone

288
00:17:33,180 --> 00:17:34,240
called Yi Chengyu?

289
00:17:38,790 --> 00:17:40,190
Does it matter

290
00:17:40,410 --> 00:17:42,840
if I do or not?

291
00:17:43,890 --> 00:17:45,310
Let me tell you a story.

292
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:47,640
It can definitely remind you of him.

293
00:17:48,980 --> 00:17:49,850
Years ago,

294
00:17:50,840 --> 00:17:53,300
there was a company called Chengyu Jewelry.

295
00:17:53,430 --> 00:17:55,270
It didn't have much influence nationwide

296
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:57,670
but dominated the local market.

297
00:17:58,030 --> 00:18:00,710
Even Ningmei had a hard time

298
00:18:01,230 --> 00:18:03,230
competing with it for market share.

299
00:18:05,870 --> 00:18:09,610
Surprisingly, the owners of these two companies

300
00:18:09,810 --> 00:18:11,450
became good friends.

301
00:18:14,710 --> 00:18:16,360
But suddenly, one day,

302
00:18:16,950 --> 00:18:19,680
Chengyu was reported for selling counterfeits.

303
00:18:19,710 --> 00:18:23,870
The media quickly followed up,

304
00:18:25,120 --> 00:18:27,950
and all kinds of negative news flooded in.

305
00:18:29,290 --> 00:18:30,310
Chengyu's store was filled with people

306
00:18:30,310 --> 00:18:32,570
protesting and returning the products.

307
00:18:33,280 --> 00:18:33,970
In the end,

308
00:18:35,270 --> 00:18:36,670
it closed down very soon.

309
00:18:39,770 --> 00:18:42,070
That happened so many years ago.

310
00:18:43,090 --> 00:18:45,040
Why did you bring it up now?

311
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:47,610
Mr. Ning, be patient.

312
00:18:48,290 --> 00:18:49,370
Hear me out.

313
00:18:54,280 --> 00:18:57,110
After Chengyu's owner, Yi Chengyu, went bankrupt,

314
00:18:57,110 --> 00:19:01,040
he was seen as an unscrupulous businessman and lived a miserable life.

315
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:02,960
His wife left him,

316
00:19:04,530 --> 00:19:06,660
and he eventually died of depression.

317
00:19:06,790 --> 00:19:09,320
Meanwhile, his good friend, Ning Zhaoxiong,

318
00:19:09,470 --> 00:19:10,970
kicked him while he was down

319
00:19:10,970 --> 00:19:13,230
and quickly took over the entire market.

320
00:19:14,870 --> 00:19:18,270
Yi Chengyu brought it upon himself by selling counterfeits.

321
00:19:18,550 --> 00:19:21,590
I merely expanded my business.

322
00:19:22,510 --> 00:19:23,910
Expanded your business?

323
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:31,630
Then how do you explain this?

324
00:19:45,940 --> 00:19:47,390
Yi Chengyu

325
00:19:48,200 --> 00:19:49,600
was my father.

326
00:19:55,850 --> 00:19:57,390
What on earth do you want?

327
00:19:57,880 --> 00:20:00,340
You'd better give me a satisfactory answer.

328
00:20:00,360 --> 00:20:01,410
Otherwise,

329
00:20:02,210 --> 00:20:03,850
I'll destroy Ningmei

330
00:20:04,280 --> 00:20:07,140
and make sure the Ning family will never have peace.

331
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:15,340
You want to expose these things,

332
00:20:16,280 --> 00:20:18,080
but given your current ability,

333
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,030
you're not capable enough to bring me down.

334
00:20:23,190 --> 00:20:24,110
I have evidence of all the illegal things

335
00:20:24,110 --> 00:20:26,750
Ningmei has been involved in over the years.

336
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,680
If you don't believe me,

337
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:30,280
just keep reading.

338
00:20:39,410 --> 00:20:42,300
You should feel relieved that I've found out

339
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:45,650
the person who spread the fake news back then wasn't you.

340
00:20:45,760 --> 00:20:48,260
The instigator who spread the fake news,

341
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:51,410
also the biggest beneficiary behind the scenes,

342
00:20:51,410 --> 00:20:52,730
was your wife,

343
00:20:53,190 --> 00:20:54,200
Chen Ling.

344
00:20:56,710 --> 00:20:57,950
I didn't expect

345
00:20:58,990 --> 00:21:02,050
Chen Ling to have done so many things behind my back.

346
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:03,430
What are you going to do?

347
00:21:07,110 --> 00:21:08,720
You must be in a great mood today.

348
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:11,550
[Floating Clouds]

349
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,110
I've slept well

350
00:21:11,150 --> 00:21:12,150
and eaten well these days.

351
00:21:12,150 --> 00:21:12,880
I feel great.

352
00:21:13,370 --> 00:21:15,540
Don't celebrate yet.

353
00:21:15,960 --> 00:21:18,390
Who knows what Ning Mochen will do next?

354
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:20,090
What can she do?

355
00:21:20,270 --> 00:21:22,790
Su Yu was the only person who could make her look good in front of Dad,

356
00:21:22,790 --> 00:21:24,450
but he's like a street rat now.

357
00:21:25,070 --> 00:21:26,200
Everyone hates him.

358
00:21:26,270 --> 00:21:29,070
I don't think she can bounce back this time.

359
00:21:29,710 --> 00:21:31,070
I didn't expect that

360
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:32,910
they were so stupid

361
00:21:32,910 --> 00:21:34,590
that they ruined themselves without us doing anything.

362
00:21:34,590 --> 00:21:35,590
How convenient.

363
00:21:36,010 --> 00:21:39,150
Anyway, you've worried a lot in the past few days, Mom.

364
00:21:39,500 --> 00:21:41,950
I bought this for you.

365
00:21:41,990 --> 00:21:42,670
Take it.

366
00:21:42,880 --> 00:21:44,500
You don't need to buy me a gift.

367
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:46,830
Just treat me well in the future.

368
00:22:04,520 --> 00:22:07,510
Why did you call me back?

369
00:22:22,140 --> 00:22:23,500
Chen, you're back.

370
00:22:23,970 --> 00:22:26,680
I thought you'd never come home.

371
00:22:27,230 --> 00:22:28,820
Chen set up the Ning family,

372
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:31,090
but she's still part of this family.

373
00:22:31,090 --> 00:22:32,550
Of course she'd come home.

374
00:22:33,540 --> 00:22:34,990
But, Mr. Su,

375
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:37,720
you're currently swamped with negative news,

376
00:22:37,720 --> 00:22:39,430
and your personal image has taken a hit.

377
00:22:39,430 --> 00:22:41,280
Not to mention the fines for contract breaches

378
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:43,920
and the pressure from public opinion across the board.

379
00:22:43,920 --> 00:22:45,990
I bet everyone in your company is disconcerted now.

380
00:22:45,990 --> 00:22:48,100
You must have a ton of issues to sort out.

381
00:22:48,100 --> 00:22:49,870
It's surprising that you've found the time

382
00:22:49,870 --> 00:22:51,400
to drop by our house.

383
00:22:52,330 --> 00:22:54,810
Dad, don't be soft-hearted.

384
00:22:55,110 --> 00:22:58,280
Although Mr. Su and my sister are engaged,

385
00:22:58,550 --> 00:23:03,470
he's notorious in the industry now.

386
00:23:03,870 --> 00:23:06,630
We need to cut ties with someone like him.

387
00:23:06,650 --> 00:23:07,450
Shut up.

388
00:23:08,070 --> 00:23:09,600
You think that's too harsh?

389
00:23:09,710 --> 00:23:10,670
Xi,

390
00:23:10,980 --> 00:23:12,950
your sister seems to

391
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:14,440
really care for Mr. Su.

392
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:18,400
She's still defending him after all he's done.

393
00:23:18,630 --> 00:23:19,630
How touching.

394
00:23:20,470 --> 00:23:23,350
It's just that Mr. Su is involved in such a scandal

395
00:23:23,350 --> 00:23:24,830
and has affected Chen.

396
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:27,100
We have to keep our distance from him.

397
00:23:27,670 --> 00:23:30,790
The reputation the Ning family has built up over the years

398
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:34,310
can't be ruined by some random guy.

399
00:23:34,990 --> 00:23:35,750
Xi,

400
00:23:36,360 --> 00:23:37,640
you can't say that.

401
00:23:38,110 --> 00:23:40,230
The Ning family always has good manners.

402
00:23:40,230 --> 00:23:41,510
No matter what others do,

403
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:43,430
we must not lose our manners.

404
00:23:43,800 --> 00:23:45,680
After all, we don't know when your sister and your brother-in-law

405
00:23:45,680 --> 00:23:47,720
will come home again.

406
00:23:48,370 --> 00:23:49,370
Are you done?

407
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:58,970
I gathered everyone here

408
00:23:59,760 --> 00:24:01,900
for a family matter.

409
00:24:07,350 --> 00:24:08,190
I declare

410
00:24:10,170 --> 00:24:12,970
that from now on, I and your stepmother, Chen Ling,

411
00:24:13,480 --> 00:24:15,760
are not long husband and wife.

412
00:24:23,000 --> 00:24:23,930
Zhaoxiong.

413
00:24:24,150 --> 00:24:25,670
Is this a joke?

414
00:24:29,580 --> 00:24:31,330
Do I look like I'm joking?

415
00:24:32,620 --> 00:24:33,300
Well…

416
00:24:35,510 --> 00:24:37,310
Did I say something too harsh just now

417
00:24:37,310 --> 00:24:38,370
and make you angry?

418
00:24:38,510 --> 00:24:39,150
Dad.

419
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:42,670
Mom cares for the Ning family,

420
00:24:42,670 --> 00:24:44,590
so she couldn't help but nag a little bit.

421
00:24:44,590 --> 00:24:46,510
Why are you so angry?

422
00:24:46,980 --> 00:24:49,140
There was a local jewelry merchant

423
00:24:49,590 --> 00:24:50,650
called Yi Chengyu.

424
00:24:51,050 --> 00:24:52,180
Do you remember him?

425
00:24:54,530 --> 00:24:57,640
That was a long time ago.

426
00:24:57,690 --> 00:24:59,640
-Why are you…
-He was a good friend of mine.

427
00:24:59,640 --> 00:25:01,300
You framed him behind my back.

428
00:25:01,590 --> 00:25:03,560
Don't you feel guilty about him and me?

429
00:25:03,560 --> 00:25:04,830
N-No.

430
00:25:04,830 --> 00:25:06,150
Why would I…

431
00:25:06,150 --> 00:25:06,990
Shut up!

432
00:25:08,390 --> 00:25:10,790
You not only did unscrupulous things

433
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:12,730
but also did them in my name

434
00:25:13,150 --> 00:25:15,080
and in the name of Ningmei Jewelry.

435
00:25:15,350 --> 00:25:15,990
Dad.

436
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:18,710
What on earth did Mom do?

437
00:25:19,710 --> 00:25:20,870
Do you know who he is?

438
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:23,750
He's Yi Chengyu's son.

439
00:25:30,070 --> 00:25:31,190
Look at these.

440
00:25:36,180 --> 00:25:37,150
Back then,

441
00:25:37,650 --> 00:25:40,270
I wanted you to acquire Chengyu Jewelry,

442
00:25:40,490 --> 00:25:43,620
but you bribed reporters and witnesses behind my back

443
00:25:44,390 --> 00:25:45,830
and accused Yi Chengyu of selling counterfeits.

444
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:46,750
You even hired thugs and idlers

445
00:25:46,750 --> 00:25:49,000
to make a scene in his store.

446
00:25:49,030 --> 00:25:51,430
How could you do such a despicable thing?

447
00:25:51,480 --> 00:25:53,270
You ruined a family!

448
00:25:57,390 --> 00:25:58,320
Ning Zhaoxiong.

449
00:25:58,530 --> 00:26:01,260
You tacitly agreed to all these things back then.

450
00:26:07,910 --> 00:26:09,870
You did something wrong,

451
00:26:09,870 --> 00:26:11,930
and worse, you left behind evidence.

452
00:26:14,270 --> 00:26:15,640
You're so useless.

453
00:26:17,440 --> 00:26:18,430
Zhaoxiong.

454
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:24,580
I've served you for so many years.

455
00:26:24,650 --> 00:26:26,620
Can you forgive me this time?

456
00:26:31,030 --> 00:26:32,310
Zhaoxiong.

457
00:26:33,940 --> 00:26:36,110
We've been married for so many years.

458
00:26:36,500 --> 00:26:38,620
How can you just divorce me like this?

459
00:26:38,640 --> 00:26:40,590
We love each other.

460
00:26:43,020 --> 00:26:44,130
My lawyer

461
00:26:44,540 --> 00:26:46,800
will talk to you later about the divorce.

462
00:26:49,740 --> 00:26:52,470
Xi, talk to your dad for me.

463
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:54,870
He's just mad at me now.

464
00:26:55,250 --> 00:26:56,010
Mom.

465
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:58,500
I can't believe someone died because of you!

466
00:26:58,940 --> 00:27:00,210
Talk to your dad for me.

467
00:27:00,550 --> 00:27:02,280
You're your dad's favorite daughter.

468
00:27:02,280 --> 00:27:03,960
He'll listen to you.

469
00:27:03,980 --> 00:27:05,510
If you leave now,

470
00:27:06,570 --> 00:27:09,060
I'll give you some money for old times' sake.

471
00:27:09,400 --> 00:27:11,210
If you keep pestering me,

472
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:13,750
I promise you won't get a penny.

473
00:27:18,680 --> 00:27:19,640
How can you…

474
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,040
Su Yu.

475
00:27:32,400 --> 00:27:34,130
Is this what you want?

476
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,860
Working in the jewelry industry.

477
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,330
Getting engaged with Ning Mochen.

478
00:27:39,790 --> 00:27:41,450
Collaborating with Ningmei.

479
00:27:42,580 --> 00:27:44,440
You've been waiting for this day.

480
00:27:44,910 --> 00:27:45,630
Yes.

481
00:28:02,870 --> 00:28:03,550
You,

482
00:28:04,190 --> 00:28:04,920
you,

483
00:28:05,150 --> 00:28:06,260
and you.

484
00:28:06,710 --> 00:28:09,990
You can all go to hell.

485
00:28:10,950 --> 00:28:12,830
You can all go to hell!

486
00:28:12,830 --> 00:28:14,510
None of you will end up well.

487
00:28:14,510 --> 00:28:15,750
You can all go to hell!

488
00:28:16,470 --> 00:28:17,830
Get your hands off me!

489
00:28:19,140 --> 00:28:20,610
You can all go to hell!

490
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:22,270
Go to hell!

491
00:28:43,930 --> 00:28:46,400
Are you satisfied with this result?

492
00:28:49,120 --> 00:28:51,720
It was because of Chen Ling that my father died.

493
00:28:52,500 --> 00:28:54,180
But you know very well

494
00:28:54,980 --> 00:28:56,460
what you have done.

495
00:29:04,260 --> 00:29:05,300
Ning Zhaoxiong.

496
00:29:07,120 --> 00:29:08,330
Behave yourself.

497
00:29:10,390 --> 00:29:10,990
Let's go.

498
00:29:36,620 --> 00:29:38,020
You're leaving already?

499
00:29:38,150 --> 00:29:38,840
Yes.

500
00:29:40,470 --> 00:29:41,270
Ning Mochen.

501
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:43,320
Thank you.

502
00:29:44,950 --> 00:29:46,000
Don't mention it.

503
00:29:46,390 --> 00:29:47,390
You helped me too.

504
00:29:49,370 --> 00:29:52,480
Thank you for helping me find evidence of Chen Ling framing my dad.

505
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:55,480
After all these years, I could finally clear his name.

506
00:29:56,350 --> 00:29:57,950
Now that Bai Li

507
00:29:57,980 --> 00:29:59,710
is in the custody of her family,

508
00:30:00,140 --> 00:30:01,600
I can finally be relieved.

509
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,390
How about you?

510
00:30:06,230 --> 00:30:07,780
You've lost a lot too.

511
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,960
How is your company now?

512
00:30:14,130 --> 00:30:15,660
It doesn't matter anymore.

513
00:30:16,230 --> 00:30:19,830
I heard from Ning Moxi that your company's reputation is damaged

514
00:30:20,510 --> 00:30:22,250
and you need to pay fines for contract breaches.

515
00:30:22,250 --> 00:30:23,580
Can you handle it alone?

516
00:30:24,190 --> 00:30:25,190
I can help you.

517
00:30:25,190 --> 00:30:25,850
No, thanks.

518
00:30:26,870 --> 00:30:28,350
Our cooperation is over.

519
00:30:28,790 --> 00:30:31,200
You have no obligation to help me anymore.

520
00:30:43,470 --> 00:30:45,070
Have you packed everything?

521
00:30:45,250 --> 00:30:46,910
Don't leave anything behind.

522
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:49,670
I didn't bring many things with me.

523
00:30:49,670 --> 00:30:52,580
Staying at your place was just a show for them.

524
00:30:53,150 --> 00:30:53,950
Now,

525
00:30:54,560 --> 00:30:56,620
we don't have to act for them anymore.

526
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,460
No.

527
00:30:59,820 --> 00:31:01,420
We don't have to act anymore.

528
00:31:03,070 --> 00:31:06,300
I'll miss the breakfast you made.

529
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:07,800
It was delicious.

530
00:31:10,310 --> 00:31:11,480
Are you hungry now?

531
00:31:15,030 --> 00:31:15,390
Yes.
